This is a two pointer question.
We need to get all sum>=lower & sum<=upper.
We need to select two numbers from array to get the sum(nums[i]+nums[j]). 



# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Approach 1
1) Select a number in the array nums[i].
2)  find another numbers in array that satisfy
 (nums[i]+nums[j]>=lower && nums[i] +nums[j]<=upper)
The second can be done using
a) brute force using for loop
